ong>and <strong>Anderson Cooper </strong>advised their colleagues against s=
uch dramatic steps. (Anderson candidly posited that, in today=E2=80=99s med=
ia landscape, there were few other places, if any, where they could go and =
produce similar work.) Some interpreted Owens=E2=80=99s remark as a dare to=
 the parentco to fire him, which might then catalyze an <em>actual</em>
