ork necessarily concurs with Owens=E2=80=99s declaration about =E2=80=9Cthe=
 edit.=E2=80=9D Even as they direct their ire toward Shari, many CBS News i=
nsiders are also frustrated with Owens for leaving them vulnerable to this =
