viously an unforced error.=E2=80=9D Several
sources said the discrepancy was preventable, and argued that Owens and <em=
>60 Minutes </em>should have taken greater care to ensure consistency betwe=
en the two interview clips, especially given the high stakes of the preside=
ntial election and the scrutiny at the time on Harris=E2=80=99s performance=
 in interviews.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p=
><p style=3D"margin:0;">In any case, folks can make their own judgments, si=
nce both F.C.C. chairman <strong>Brendan Carr </strong>and
<em>60 Minutes </em>made the <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWF=
pbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dVMk9EdnNmU1BEb2kwS25RNlp3WT0iLCJocmVmIj=
